data.description: Welcome to Creek Preserve community not far from the SouthShore metro lagoon.  Pulling into the driveway you will find that this home has upgraded Lanscaping with rocks and shrubbery. This Beautiful home offers a nice neutral canvas that is already built and ready to go along with lots of space to grow. Your future home sits on a conservation lot with no neighbor behind. Entering from the front door you will find the staircase to the right and a hallway to the spacious open floor plan encompassing the kitchen, living and dining room. Through the kitchen to the right is the downstairs bedroom and the bathroom directly across. Main living space offers a large size living room with a dining room/kitchen combo. This home brings in natural lights that flow through this open floor plan. The stunning kitchen has plenty of space for entertainment with a huge island. The kitchen also offers granite counter tops and stainless-steel appliances. The Homeowner has added a backsplash to the kitchen adding a bit of personal touch. Upstairs you will find a cozy loft area that could be used to place a desk for an office or to place nice decor for a sitting area. The master bedroom sits slightly away from the remaining three bedrooms. This home also has a beautiful resort style community pool not far from the home's location. Please reach out to book a showing we would love to work with you to make this your next move.
